com.intel.icecp.node.channels.ndn.notification

Class NdnChannelPublisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.icecp.node.channels.ndn.notification.NdnChannelPublisher

  • public class NdnChannelPublisher
extends Object
    Manage all publishing of Messages on an NdnNotificationChannel; this class is now factored out into MessageCache and MessageRequestHandler for use with other channel types.

        prefix - the NDN prefix of the channel; for building response packets and filtering
        pipeline - the operations necessary for converting Messages to bytes for transmission
        pool - the thread pool in which to run the encoding and transmission tasks
        marker - the NDN component tag identifying a message ID

        filterable - the object on which to add the NDN filters
